	  - if( !( SourceFail ) == RedeAnterior ) + if( RedeAnterior == !(
	  SourceFail ) )  given this assignment just below the if-clause:
	  RedeAnterior = !( SourceFail );  to avoid a compiler warning that
	  "!" might apply not in a way intended by author
