	* drivers/usbhid-ups.c: usbhid-ups.c: fall back to HID Input type if
	  not a Feature

2015-06-07  Charles Lepple <clepple+nut@gmail.com>

	* drivers/tripplite-hid.c: tripplite-hid.c: device.part is static
	  (version 0.82)

