2013-10-02  Arnaud Quette <arnaud.quette@free.fr>

	* data/driver.list.in: [HCL] Add support for Eaton 5S  Add Eaton 5S
	  (USB ID 0x0463:0xffff) to the list of usbhid-ups supported models
