2013-02-01  Arnaud Quette <arnaud.quette@free.fr>

	* docs/man/snmp-ups.txt: Update SNMP driver documentation  Mentioning
	  'mib' is not needed anymore since NUT 2.6.2. Also mention 'v3' as
